r two trails using Action Bound or similar which act as a bridge between students studying at Brooks building and local community.<\/p>\n<p>Or<a href=\"http:\/\/www.edlab.org.uk\/submit-edlab-project\/\"> submit us a proposal<\/a> with your ideas and contacts <a href=\"http:\/\/www.edlab.org.uk\/submit-edlab-project\/\">on this page of our website.<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The use of maps can stimulate learning experiences and increase engagement. MMU has a history of experimenting with games and apps with an aim to increase student engagement. We can add to this work by creating challenges in the form of Treasure Hunts or Adventure Trails aimed at both young people and adults. The use [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":29,"featured_media":1050,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[41,128,129],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v15.6.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/action-bound\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"EdLab Spark: Create an Activity or Story Trail - EdLab MMU\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"The use of maps can stimulate learning experiences and increase engagement. MMU has a history of experimenting with games and apps with an aim to increase student engagement. We can add to this work by creating challenges in the form of Treasure Hunts or Adventure Trails aimed at both young people and adults. The use [&hellip;]\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/action-bound\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_nam